{"tid":2509711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巨型運牛船遇颱風 日本海翻沉  5867隻牛下落不明","createTime":"2021-04-29T15:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T15:50:35.000Z","uid":49648,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4accc4e4394bbc97aa24fecf85719da207d5d779","tid":2509711,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"活體動物運輸船遇颱風 日本海域翻覆 42人5867牛下落不明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYyjBvTx7ky2YBbDNqwmmEPZrjQZkjmKn2LeQALP9vkpC?filename=hB9Pz0s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhB9Pz0s.jpg&h=2b509366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者 李娉婷/報導<br />\n<br />\n又有活體動物運輸船發生重大意外！9月2日，從紐西蘭出發、原預定於3日抵達中國的「海灣牲畜1號」（Gulf Livestock 1）在穿越日本海域時，被颱風帶來的巨浪掀翻，截至4日清晨，全船43名船員和5,867隻活牛中，仍只有1人獲救，這起悲劇，也讓「活體出口」（Live export，將活體經濟動物出口到其他國家）的諸多問題，再次浮現於公眾視野。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旅途中遇上颱風大浪，意外翻覆的海灣牲畜1號。   取自NZ Herald（Photo / Tony des Landes）<br />\n8月14日，海灣牲畜1號從紐西蘭北島的港市內皮爾（Napier）出發，預計將在9月3日抵達中國唐山港，然而，在即將抵達目的地前，該貨輪行經路線卻受到颱風梅莎（Maysak）影響，9月2日凌晨，海灣牲畜1號在距離日本奄美大島西方約185公里處的東海海域發出求救訊號，日本派出了3架巡邏機和4搜海巡船，但經過近24小時的救援任務後，救援人員只找到了現年45歲、菲律賓籍的大副Sareno Edvardo，其餘42名船員及5,867隻活牛皆下落不明。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，43名船員中，有39名為菲律賓籍、2名為紐西蘭籍、2名為澳洲籍（另有報導指出為1名澳洲籍、1名新加坡籍），此外，<a href=\"http://根據船舶追蹤網站VesselFinder.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9A%E8%88%B9%E8%88%B6%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99VesselFinder.com&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=c6ef32a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">根據船舶追蹤網站VesselFinder.com</a>的資料，456英尺長的海灣牲畜1號建造於2002年，並於巴拿馬註冊。日本海上保安廳發言人援引Edvardo的說法表示，該貨輪的一個引擎在意外發生前就已失靈，接著船隻在惡劣的天氣中，被海浪擊沉。<br />\n<br />\n啲牛去晒邊，好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697435d567e8df4ed033d6e32389cdf2c3d03f6d","tid":2509711,"uid":117584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1a625abc9975ec863f03c7a1b408ba791601e3","tid":2509711,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67ba3d1352e56428a38b824e0e420f1f4482431","tid":2509711,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea433e6f58053f6dba3e0be12434205c9b9d31f7","tid":2509711,"uid":47042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>2020年9月3日</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>舊聞，BLOCK，未推</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"910ae1f065dc9b4443c18a1200c4e105ca4e970b","tid":2509711,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ea433e6f58053f6dba3e0be12434205c9b9d31f7","tid":2509711,"uid":47042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>2020年9月3日</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>舊聞，BLOCK，未推</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":1